                <p>The Altroz facelift continues with Tata’s familiar variant structure—<span class="font-weight-700">XE, XM, XT, XZ, and XZ+</span>, while adding new trims like <span class="font-weight-700">XZ Lux</span> and <span class="font-weight-700">XZ+ S</span> with added features. </p>
                <ul>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Starting Price:</span> ₹6.89 lakh (Ex-showroom) </li>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Top-end trims (turbo petrol/DCT)</span> could go beyond ₹10 lakh </li>
                </ul>
